---
layout: layout.njk
title: Contact Us
---

<div class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>We'd love to hear from you. Whether you have a question about our services, want to discuss a potential project, or just want to say hello, please don't hesitate to get in touch.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p><i class="fas fa-user"></i> <strong>{{ site.contact.name }}</strong> - {{ site.contact.title }}</p>
            <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phone }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a></p>
            <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a></p>
            <p><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.contact.whatsapp }}" target="_blank">Chat on WhatsApp</a></p>
            <p><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i> <a href="{{ site.contact.facebook }}" target="_blank">Follow us on Facebook</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
